CommunicationModuleOwner, PerceptionModuleOwner, ElectricVehicleOperatingSystem, AdHocCommunicative, CellCommunicative, Locatable, Navigable, Perceptive, OperatingSystem, VehicleOperatingSystem, EventProcessor
public class ElectricVehicleUnit extends VehicleUnit implements ElectricVehicleOperatingSystem
This class represents an electric vehicle in the application simulator. It extends VehicleUnit with further functionality.
